  "compassievolle-pauze": "compassionate-pause",
  "Complimenteer jezelf daarna: dit was goed voor jou.": "Then compliment yourself: this was good for you.",
  "Concept automatisch opgeslagen.": "Draft saved automatically.",
  "Concept wordt zo opgeslagen…": "Draft is saved like this…",
